Subject: [PATCH AUTOSEL 5.15 19/20] net/smc: reduce rtnl pressure in smc_pnet_create_pnetids_list()
Date: Fri, 29 Mar 2024 08:33:07 -0400
Message-ID: <20240329123316.3085691-19-sashal@kernel.org>
